ext-empty-paragraph""><br/></p><figure data-size=""normal""><img src=""https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a6e37cc819c424c98158db9dd1c8d97c_hd.jpg"" data-rawwidth=""1136"" data-rawheight=""640"" data-size=""normal"" data-caption="""" data-default-watermark-src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-9670be72315587bc433e05d3cc9fc5fc_hd.jpg"" class=""origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb"" width=""1136"" data-original=""https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a6e37cc819c424c98158db9dd1c8d97c_r.jpg""/></figure><p>年轻人似乎未全get到任先生的 “大智谋”，举凡研究过 <a href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E5%259F%2583%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%258A%25A0%25C2%25B7%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25AF%25BA/82327%3Ffromtitle%3DEdgar%2520Snow%26fromid%3D12003144%26fr%3Daladdin"" class="" wrap external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer"">Edgar Snow</a> 捉刀造册时期的长者，解读时必该 穿透画皮，拨沙取金。（略.....若干字，见图）</p><figure data-size=""normal""><img src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-15dc6956773e70956230454bafa878b2_hd.jpg"" data-rawwidth=""803"" data-rawheight=""454"" data-size=""normal"" data-caption="""" data-default-watermark-src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-20fb3b11b7b8b84bd2f2033d56a2ca80_hd.jpg"" class=""origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb"" width=""803"" data-original=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-15dc6956773e70956230454bafa878b2_r.jpg""/></figure><p>在内 HW活路无忧。会被包装为 邓先生自改革开放以来，鼓励涌现的“民企” hightech旗帜和“四个自信”的倔强脸庞，亦如是中国版的too big to fail. 信号设备解决方案有专利加持，并无 时间线下 抒情帮 描述的悲壮凄沧。不定还得谢HiSilicon 令新机开辟出 豪华暖手宝 的附赠功能。不失时机地推出蛰伏的鸿蒙系统，更为行业<a href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//baijiahao.baidu.com/s%3Fid%3D1627060872500073325%26wfr%3Dspider%26for%3Dpc%26isFailFlag%3D1"" class="" wrap external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer"">增智慧</a>。</p><p><a href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//twitter.com/i/status/1133235235628494849"" class="" external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer""><span class=""invisible"">https://</span><span class=""visible"">twitter.com/i/status/11</span><span class=""invisible"">33235235628494849</span><span class=""ellipsis""></span></a></p><figure data-size=""normal""><img src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-991f28a7b54963e5e530b81a7a2ef1ef_hd.jpg"" data-rawwidth=""1483"" data-rawheight=""951"" data-size=""normal"" data-default-watermark-src=""https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-0ca1e02a90352f0c7ee0e6f9fe9e1882_hd.jpg"" class=""origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb"" width=""1483"" data-original=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-991f28a7b54963e5e530b81a7a2ef1ef_r.jpg""/></figure><p class=""ztext-empty-paragraph""><br/></p><figure data-size=""normal""><img src=""https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-675fdf7f5f58e42c5bb33271da8221a8_hd.jpg"" data-rawwidth=""1481"" data-rawheight=""953"" data-size=""normal"" data-default-watermark-src=""https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b624f65c7b2f13e58c83e66bedee2c3_hd.jpg"" class=""origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb"" width=""1481"" data-original=""https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-675fdf7f5f58e42c5bb33271da8221a8_r.jpg""/></figure><p>在外，固然美国时下软硬兼施行政禁令，然而美律文规章 照旧支持下游厂商隔1~2月单次定量申购渠道，即使难保会被提价，频繁申请蛮困扰，未必次次应允审过，但此时经年仍存活力。 </p><figure data-size=""normal""><img src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-55c61b2d2e5fd3750c6d659aa7236dfe_hd.jpg"" data-rawwidth=""694"" data-rawheight=""723"" data-size=""normal"" data-caption="""" data-default-watermark-src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-30bdb1306c28e579229f14f36603bebf_hd.jpg"" class=""origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb"" width=""694"" data-original=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-55c61b2d2e5fd3750c6d659aa7236dfe_r.jpg""/></figure><p><a href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//dis.myzaker.com/wap/v2/%3Fdiscussion_id%3D156%26post_id%3D58f7333fd1f1490656000093"" class="" external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer""><span class=""invisible"">http://</span><span class=""visible"">dis.myzaker.com/wap/v2/?</span><span class=""invisible"">discussion_id=156&amp;post_id=58f7333fd1f1490656000093</span><span class=""ellipsis""></span></a> </p><p>愚昧诳语笼罩的纪元似渐远离，世道本非你幻境。享受着骨干网、强大功能的手机的公/私用户，<b>不会忘记HW 降低地球人通信成本 的卓越贡献，也不会忘拆台 </b><a href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ZTE"" class="" wrap external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer"">ZTE</a><b> /MI，又伙同 /<i>Cisco /</i></b><a href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Radio_and_Television_Administration"" class="" wrap external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer"">SARFT</a><b><i>…… 提供</i></b><a href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1984"" class="" wrap external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer"">《1984》</a><b><i>配套</i>服务</b>。（结语时，<a href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.theguardian.com/"" class="" wrap external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer"">The Guardian</a> 、<a href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/"" class="" wrap external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer"">Washington Pos</a>t 相继中招， 省略若干）</p><p>实话不吐不快，是超越国界和民族的凡人善意的本性。抹黑资料多了，势必有人踊跃反驳。自然也另有部分人受不了雄文蛊惑，而纠错降温，避遭魔怔。</p><figure data-size=""normal""><img src=""https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-40cef19b0ead7969e9d946351800486b_hd.jpg"" data-rawwidth=""1080"" data-rawheight=""607"" data-size=""normal"" data-caption="""" data-default-watermark-src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-172de3c8e1fdf07279f4cc98e7d5c6ed_hd.jpg"" class=""origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb"" width=""1080"" data-original=""https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-40cef19b0ead7969e9d946351800486b_r.jpg""/></figure><figure data-size=""normal""><img src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d0cf652c85064652400830522a7eade3_hd.jpg"" data-rawwidth=""1080"" data-rawheight=""607"" data-size=""normal"" data-caption="""" data-default-watermark-src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d6c5960e61001a5abfc107c33e93cc65_hd.jpg"" class=""origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb"" width=""1080"" data-original=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d0cf652c85064652400830522a7eade3_r.jpg""/></figure><figure data-size=""normal""><img src=""https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a3a2cd51631ee716c5d4dc64cd8ae902_hd.jpg"" data-rawwidth=""1080"" data-rawheight=""607"" data-size=""normal"" data-caption="""" data-default-watermark-src=""https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ab92e421c2c49083696a3c2215c2b96b_hd.jpg"" class=""origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb"" width=""1080"" data-original=""https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a3a2cd51631ee716c5d4dc64cd8ae902_r.jpg""/></figure><p>关注中外 互联网 数十载有余的盆友，记忆是连续的，也忘不了光环笼罩的实体 从热血青年 蜕变 傲娇流氓 的黑色幽默。</p><a data-draft-node=""block"" data-draft-type=""link-card"" href=""https://www.zhihu.com/question/66101490/answer/239889535"" class=""internal"">为什么中国的互联网流氓软件横行？</a><a data-draft-node=""block"" data-draft-type=""link-card"" href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.theverge.com/2019/4/10/18304739/facebook-groups-reduce-misinformation-harmful-content-changes-messenger"" data-image=""https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c32e01dafb2dc045ff18d8ff0d23ffc2_180x120.jpg"" data-image-width=""1200"" data-image-height=""628"" class="" wrap external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer"">Facebook will punish groups for repeatedly spreading fake news</a><p>线上不海军狗咬狗/线下不同行台拆台，广告诚实，价格合理品质安全，服务省心、功能主流的产品，谁不爱呢。</p><a data-draft-node=""block"" data-draft-type=""link-card"" href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.guancha.cn/Neighbors/2015_04_01_314441.shtml"" data-image=""https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ef82a06a7317800409809f4fc46bcae4_120x160.jpg"" data-image-width=""300"" data-image-height=""398"" class="" wrap external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer"">俄罗斯小伙卧底“网络水军中心” 揭露俄罗斯官方如何操纵舆论</a><a data-draft-node=""block"" data-draft-type=""link-card"" href=""https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//foreignpolicy.com/2015/06/17/how-to-spot-a-state-funded-chinese-internet-troll/"" class="" external"" target=""_blank"" rel=""nofollow noreferrer""><span class=""invisible"">https://</span><span class=""visible"">foreignpolicy.com/2015/</span><span class=""invisible"">06/17/how-to-spot-a-state-funded-chinese-internet-troll/</span><span class=""ellipsis""></span></a>